kingun-device-spray-stem-cells-wounds/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frenovacareinc.com%2F2016%2F12%2Frenovacare-awarded-u-s-patent-skingun-device-spray-stem-cells-wounds%2F&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=285e3044\" target=\"_blank\">http://renovacareinc.com/2016/12/renovacare-awarded-u-s-patent-skingun-device-spray-stem-cells-wounds/</a><br />\n<br />\n有個儀器啱啱攞咗patent無耐　可能好貴　但我相信錢唔係問題　一呼百應<br />\n最怕係香港醫療系統怕柒，明明有更佳處理選項，但可能因為要求援於日本啊美國啊而冇考慮，又未必有講畀病人知</blockquote><br />\n呢d 有排都未過到醫管局，係香港唔會用得，一用就犯法</blockquote><br />\n咁有咩辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通坐醫療專機飛去美國做咩　貴上加貴<br />\n最怕係架公司吹大左成效　到時錢就畀左　人又絕望<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2016/12/07/health/skingun-burn-care-technologies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2Fhealth%2Fskingun-burn-care-technologies&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=587ac3b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2Fhealth%2Fskingun-burn-care-technologies&h=af6a0cf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2016/12/07/health/skingun-burn-care-technologies</a> CNN話阿根廷有個人親身試驗緊呢個技術喎<br />\n雖然連美國FDA都未批　　但有無辦法令嗰間公司喺今次災難嘅傷者身上做試驗　咁唔係fit哂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走佬去台灣醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}